model.name: Fall Guys Model Pack
model.description: An unofficial Beat Saber Fall Guys model pack! This model pack contains: platforms, notes, sabers, walls, and hitsounds. It also includes maps of the entire Fall Guys OST. If you're confused on how to install this pack, click the Installation button for instructions.

model.name: DDR Saber
model.description: A Beat Saber model pack that adds DDR notes and platforms. This model pack is meant to be used with Feet Saber, so download Naluluna modifiers if you haven't already. It also comes with a mod that modifies the note rotation to be more realistic.

model.name: Minecraft Wall Pack
model.description: The Beat Saber Minecraft wall pack contains 10 walls. 3 are animated, and 2 have custom colors.

model.name: Matrix Code
model.description:
"The Matrix is everywhere. It is all around us."
These walls have a really cool matrix code effect.

model.name: Step Back Wall
model.description:
A blast to the past. If you remember what these are, you are eligible for a veteran's discount.

This model contains two versions: one uses camera distance to simulate the original step back wall effect, and the other one uses the normal texture.
